1
00:00:59,240 --> 00:01:00,080
So.

2
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:04,200
So you want me to replace him.

3
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:07,000
You are very smart,

4
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,240
Mr. He.

5
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:10,660
But you won't be doing it for nothing.

6
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:14,640
As long as you sign it,

7
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,440
the Gu Group

8
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:19,330
will give you a 5-million settlement allowance.

9
00:01:20,039 --> 00:01:20,840
Five million.

10
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,080
What, not enough?

11
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:25,160
Then 10 million,

12
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:30,200
plus a 500-square-meter apartment with a view in the Binhai CBD.

13
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:31,520
How about it?

14
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:32,250
Chairman Gu,

15
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:33,780
I didn't mean that.

16
00:01:34,479 --> 00:01:35,640
Then what are you waiting for?

17
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:36,770
Hurry up and sign it.

18
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:39,120
Sorry.

19
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:41,200
I have no interest in participating

20
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:43,060
in your deceitful business wars.

21
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:43,890
Goodbye.

22
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:50,400
You guys.

23
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,280
Mr. He.

24
00:01:58,640 --> 00:02:00,640
I just want to discuss this with you.

25
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:02,240
Don't make it difficult for me.

26
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:02,840
Is this

27
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:04,930
how you discuss things?

28
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,400
Okay.

29
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:07,720
Okay, okay, okay.

30
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:08,440
I agree.

31
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:09,280
Luo Xin,

32
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:10,680
let him go.

33
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:24,280
These are the people

34
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,800
Young Master Haoran usually interacts with.

35
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,460
Take a look.

36
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:37,290
Why does this girl look exactly like Zixi?

37
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:39,610
Chairman Gu.

38
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,650
Who is this girl?

39
00:02:42,480 --> 00:02:44,840
She is the daughter of the Chen Group,

40
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,360
named Chen Ziqing.

41
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,960
She is also Haoran's crush.

42
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:52,840
Chen Group, Chen Ziqing.

43
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:54,320
Could it be

44
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:57,490
that Zixi was also born on this day?

45
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,370
It seems my guess was right.

46
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,760
They are indeed twin sisters.

47
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:05,200
Are they officially dating?

48
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:07,720
This Chen Ziqing is very stubborn.

49
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:11,320
She is set on becoming a female racer

50
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:15,220
and wants to participate in our Dragon Country Grand Prix.

51
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:17,010
With Haoran's driving skills,

52
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:19,100
she doesn't even take him seriously.

53
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:21,010
So don't even expect

54
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:23,160
her to date Haoran.

55
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:26,960
The Dragon Country Grand Prix is very complicated.

56
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:29,820
I can't let Zixi's sister repeat the same mistakes.

57
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:30,600
(P Besides,

58
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,160
Besides,

59
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,490
if I pretend to be Gu Haoran,

60
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:36,329
I might be able to get some clues

61
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,490
from Zixi's sister.

62
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:40,660
After all, she is Zixi's only sister.

63
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:44,880
Okay.

64
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,280
I promise you.

65
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:47,800
I can play Gu Haoran.

66
00:03:49,079 --> 00:03:50,200
That's great.

67
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:51,640
However,

68
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:54,800
you changed your mind so quickly, Mr. He.

69
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,880
Could it be that you fell in love

70
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:59,200
at first sight with the person in the photo?

71
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:00,000
If so,

72
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:01,400
if you can

73
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:04,740
facilitate the marriage between the Gu and Chen families,

74
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:07,200
I will reward you handsomely in the future.

75
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:10,560
This is the senior security team leader of the Gu Group,

76
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:11,720
Luo Xin.

77
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:15,640
From now on, she will be your private secretary and bodyguard.

78
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,399
Sorry if I offended you earlier.

79
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:20,200
My apologies.

80
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:22,760
It's fine.

81
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,490
Starting today,

82
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:26,480
I will call you Young Master.

83
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:28,450
Let's go.

84
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,400
I'll take you to get changed.

85
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:33,840
Is it necessary to play the role in such a hurry?

86
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,200
Yes.

87
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,520
Today you will take my young master's place

88
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:39,320
to accompany Miss Chen for a test drive.

89
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:39,850
Let's go.

90
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:32,840
Young Master, we have arrived at the Chen residence.

91
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:34,040
Remember what I said.

92
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:36,680
Don't blow your cover in front of Miss Chen,

93
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:39,159
otherwise, the consequences will be severe.

94
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:39,890
At 5:00 p.m.,

95
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:42,050
I'll pick you up at the dealership.

96
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:42,880
Okay.

97
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:07,840
Gu Haoran, what are you staring at?

98
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,440
My sister-in-law,

99
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,120
Chen Ziqing.

100
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:28,340
Hold it.

101
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,409
What do you mean?

102
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:39,040
Don't think being the CEO of Gu Group

103
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,400
makes you a big deal.

104
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:41,880
I wouldn't fall for a man

105
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:44,210
whose driving skills are worse than mine.

106
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:48,400
Pick up my bag now.

107
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:52,320
She looks exactly like her sister.

108
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,159
Hurry up.

109
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:58,690
I still need to go to Yaosheng Dealership.

110
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:00,760
Coming.

111
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,640
Miss Chen, this way, please.

112
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,160
Here are

113
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:18,000
all our JDM models.

114
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:20,280
See if there's any you like.

115
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:38,320
Isn't this an RX-7 FD?

116
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,380
The one from Initial D.

117
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:41,360
Yes, Miss Chen.

118
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,490
You have a great eye.

119
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:43,360
This one is indeed

120
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:45,280
the same model as Ryosuke Takahashi's.

121
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:45,880
Moreover,

122
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:48,560
it is currently a rare global limited edition.

123
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:12,120
This is a 280-hp twin-turbo rotary engine.

124
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,440
The power is indeed strong,

125
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,440
but it lacks grip.

126
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:16,160
Its cornering problem is too fatal.

127
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:17,820
It is not suitable for racing.

128
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,920
What do you know, you amateur?

129
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,900
I'll take this one.

130
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:26,560
Okay, Ms. Chen.

131
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:28,820
I'll issue the invoice for you right now.

132
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,010
Get down.

133
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,400
I told you to get down.

134
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:36,980
Didn't you hear me?

135
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:20,300
If it weren't for your sister,

136
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:22,240
I wouldn't take this crap.

137
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:29,020
Bring the shoes for me.

138
00:10:47,040 --> 00:10:48,480
The mountain road ahead is full of sharp turns.

139
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:50,280
It's not suitable for drifting.

140
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:52,040
Excuse me,

141
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,540
please let me through.

142
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:02,040
Gu Haoran.

143
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:04,560
Don't you think it's dangerous to get in my car?

144
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:06,240
I got in to protect you.

145
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:08,090
Alright.

146
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,440
You asked for this.

147
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:11,770
Don't throw up in the car later.

148
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:29,120
Left foot.

149
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:52,080
With your skills,

150
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:54,400
you dare to drive on mountain roads?

151
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,780
We really lost face this time.

152
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:17,660
On the way down,

153
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:18,600
let me drive.

154
00:13:21,160 --> 00:13:22,690
When did you learn to drift?

155
00:13:23,560 --> 00:13:24,490
Just learned it.

156
00:13:25,280 --> 00:13:26,040
Put me down.

157
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:29,370
What do you mean?

158
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,650
You asked me to put you down.

159
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:40,600
Ding Wen.

160
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,280
Gu Haoran.

161
00:13:47,680 --> 00:13:49,740
You haven't fallen to your death yet?

162
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,960
I was born lucky.

163
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,280
I survived.
